SUMMARY:Saturday Night Mass
DESCRIPTION:Usually presented on the second Saturday of the month\, these masses offer something new and surprising to inspire and challenge you in your faith journey. A broad array of live music features favorite artists from the past\, contemporary artists and contemplative themes while being integrated into traditional Episcopal liturgy. \n  \nMost Saturday Night Masses are streamed and can be viewed from our website by clicking here. \n 
